Package com.ibm.util.merge.data

The DataManager class that provides path-based access to an abstract Object Data structure.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataElement
    A DataElement is the abstract base for the IDMU Data Object structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataList
    The DataList object represents a list of values in the DataManager
    DataManager
    The data manager provides a path based interface to the Data Element structure
    DataObject
    Represents an Object (Map of unique String to Value pairs)
    DataPrimitive
    Represents a primitive (String) Data Element
    Path
    Represents a path to an element of the Data Manger.
    PathPart
    Represents a single member of a data path
